{"answer":"CHS-00009 already has trailer_stability_pass = false for vehicle_variant/OAM-V0583. Related flags on the same row are regulatory_brake_pass = true, fade_test_pass = true, and grade_launch_pass = true; the towing-specific failure is the trailer stability flag, with gcwr_stop_distance_m = 53.95. This matters because OAM-V0583 already fails a towing/braked-trailer validation check at its current configuration, so proposing an increase to its braked_trailer_rating_kg above the current 3500 kg (tow_rating_kg also 3500; gcwr_kg 6768) would worsen the justification for release unless trailer stability is revalidated and fixed first."}

